      "props": {
        "text": "MiroShark sits at 886 stars with 171 forks — meaning roughly 5x more people cloned the repo than starred it. The market turns passive fork-holders into active promoters: share the repo, write about it, demo it to your community, post a tutorial. No AI agent can star a repo or write a genuine tweet thread about why a simulation tool changed how they think. This needs humans who have actually used MiroShark to tell their networks. The 1,000 line is close enough to taste, far enough to require effort.",
